  "body": "<p data-start=\"99\" data-end=\"261\"><strong>💥 TNT Arrow</strong><br data-start=\"111\" data-end=\"114\">TNT Arrow is a lightweight Minecraft data pack that adds craftable explosive arrows, perfect for blasting mobs, mining, or causing mayhem at range.</p>\n<p data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"519\"><strong data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"275\">Features</strong><br data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"278\">&bull; Craftable using 1 Arrow + 1 TNT<br data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"314\">&bull; Arrows explode on impact or when grounded<br data-start=\"357\" data-end=\"360\">&bull;Minecraft 1.17+</p>\n<p data-start=\"263\" data-end=\"519\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1235/548/pi7_gif_cmp-6-gif.gif\"></p>",
